{"tid":279500,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同個fd去游水 我都未出聲佢就幫我入咗5蚊……","createTime":"2017-06-11T10:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T14:17:47.000Z","uid":13701,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd417e35df243caab7ea19d42175399934fd0445","tid":279500,"uid":13701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"我啱啱伸隻手入個袋佢就幫我入咗5蚊落個locker<br />\n跟住話：未出發！先興奮～<br />\n咁都算喇唔係咩大不了嘅野<br />\n<br />\n但係游水嗰陣我游得慢，條撚樣喺我後面成日撞鳩我，叫佢游前面佢又話：<br />\n「前面隻眼先可以睇實你」<br />\n屌我游得慢姐又唔係唔識游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身仲話游完上佢屋企打機<br />\n而家游撚到成肚火游完就返咗屋企，5蚊都唔記得坽<br />\n啱啱佢打嚟話我未俾返個5蚊佢仲約我聽日再游或者上佢屋企打機順便俾返佢<br />\n仆街唔想出都焗住要去，我諗住去打機算，5蚊當去網吧玩一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1856418525fe9a00eb04a0e72e24e79de13f6aa3","tid":279500,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"6e293f146221dd3c32a5f86f8a21ddf1e7b36358","tid":279500,"uid":68867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3de24c2d192382e5fa6625b652d62f51a9a8029","tid":279500,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"GAY，完！"},{"pid":"f6cfd924bd71981afdabc50e274e981142d28b4e","tid":279500,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GAY，完！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"67d573f1b38ed8b41fc7606f2207922ae0e33805","tid":279500,"uid":8243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"留名加甜"},{"pid":"1fe83599d4ec71c4a80552d32a3985da124aafdd","tid":279500,"uid":13701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote